    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who make historical sense of the natural sciences by employing textual, ethnographic, and social scientific methods to investigate how the sciences work in practice, and how they relate to larger intellectual, cultural, social, and political trends and changes.</Note_Text>
